20 PENCOLOR 'RED
30 FILLBOX 200 200 (-200) 0
40 PENCOLOR 'BLUE
50 FILLBOX 200 200 0 0
60 PENCOLOR 'GREEN
70 FILLBOX 200 200 200 0
80 SLEEP 4
90 REPLACECOLOR 'BLUE :ERASERCOLOR
100 MAKE 'CD 200
110 ERASERUP SETX - (100 + :CD) SETY 100 ERASERDOWN DELY (-200) ERASERUP
120 SETX :CD + 100 ERASERDOWN DELY 200 ERASERUP
130 SETX :CD - 100 PENDOWN PENCOLOR 'GREEN DELY (-200) PENUP
140 SETX 100 - :CD PENDOWN PENCOLOR 'RED DELY 200 PENUP
150 MAKE 'CD :CD - 1
